      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 06:47:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>几内亚石油码头爆炸至少11人死亡；损害程度尚不清楚</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/several-feared-killed-guinea-oil-terminal-blast-police-officer-2023-12-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几内亚首都科纳克里一处石油码头周一凌晨发生爆炸，造成至少 11 人死亡、88 人受伤，民防部门负责人让·特拉奥雷 (Jean Traore) 表示，政府警告称，该事件可能会直接影响该国民众。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/several-feared-killed-guinea-oil-terminal-blast-police-officer-2023-12-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 06:28:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国防部长驻以色列推动缓解加沙攻势强度</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/israeli-forces-launch-strikes-up-down-gaza-strip-hospital-hit-2023-12-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于平民死亡和巴勒斯坦人的饥饿不断增加，以色列周一面临来访的美国国防部长的压力和全球人权组织的谴责，原因是以色列与加沙哈马斯的战争激烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/israeli-forces-launch-strikes-up-down-gaza-strip-hospital-hit-2023-12-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 02:53:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜在谴责美国“战争”举动后发射洲际弹道导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-fires-ballistic-missile-south-korea-says-2023-12-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国和日本表示，朝鲜周一发射了一枚洲际弹道导弹，射程可覆盖美国任何地方，这是几小时内的第二次发射，平壤谴责美国主导的武力展示是“战争”的举动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-fires-ballistic-missile-south-korea-says-2023-12-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 23:37:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及塞西：热衷于桥梁的独裁领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/egypts-sisi-authoritarian-leader-with-penchant-bridges-2023-12-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及总统阿卜杜勒·法塔赫·塞西因镇压短暂民主时期残存的反对派而被批评为暴君，同时因加强安全和推动军队领导的基础设施建设而赢得支持者的赞扬。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/egypts-sisi-authoritarian-leader-with-penchant-bridges-2023-12-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 14:22:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
